Enable alternative userspace recipes

When the system has multiple versions of userspace recipes available,
a stable and an indevelopment 'next' version.  Switch to enabling the next
version of selected packages.

This template will focus on enabling new versions of recipes where ABI and
API changes are expected.

#@TYPE: Wrtemplate
#@NAME: userspace-next
#@DESCRIPTION: Enable alternative in-development (future) userspace recipes

